    • Field Detail

      • ADDRESS_BITS

        static final String ADDRESS_BITS
        The number of address bits to use (default DEFAULT_ADDRESS_BITS ). The fan-out of the HTree will be 2^addressBits. A value of 10 will have a fan-out of 1024 and the resulting page size will be in 4 ~ 8k.
        See Also:
        DEFAULT_ADDRESS_BITS
